#, fuzzy
msgid "Splitting Skullache"
msgstr "裂颅之痛"

#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You have bested so many of us skeletons in battle, Dragon Rider.  Now I need "
"your help.  Bring me the skulls of my fallen comrades, and I will reward you "
"for your trouble."
msgstr ""
"你在战斗中击败了我们许多同族，龙骑士。现在我需要你的帮助：将阵亡同伴的头骨带来，我会给予你酬谢。"

#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You can bring me up to ten skulls per day.  When I am satisfied, I will "
"share an intriguing object I found with you."
msgstr ""
"你每天最多可交给我十个头骨。当我满意时，我会将一件有趣的物品交给你。"

#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Alas, poor Yorick.  I knew him, Dragon Rider.  Thank you for these skulls."
msgstr ""
"唉，可怜的约里克！我曾与他相识，龙骑士。感谢你带来这些头骨。"

#, fuzzy
msgid "Tell the Skeleton you have the skulls."
msgstr "告诉多嘴骷髅你已收集到头骨。"

#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Now that we have gathered the skulls of my comrades, I can be at peace.  "
"Thank you, Dragon Rider.  As promised, here is your reward.  I hope you can "
"put it to good use."
msgstr ""
"既然战友的头骨已经收集齐，我也可以安心了。谢谢你，龙骑士。如约，这是你的奖励。愿你善加利用。"
